<p>A new Master of Science in the Computeel Group: <a href="/team/DoriniThiago.html">Thiago Dorini</a> has successfully presented his dissertation <em>“The defect structure of the T1 and T2 phases in the Cr-Si-B system”</em>, obtaining therefore his MSci. degree in our department.</p>

<p>Hopefully, his work will soon be published as a paper (or more than one!) in an international journal so that the world at large can appreciate his contributions.</p>

<p>Thiago will soon be going to France to start his PhD studies at the Institute Jean Lamour, Université de Lorraine, under the supervision of <a href="http://emiliegaudry.perso.univ-lorraine.fr/">Prof. Emily Gaudry</a>.</p>

<p>Good luck and a lot of success!</p>
:ET